data.description: WOW! Spacious and well maintained end unit on a Cul-de-sac lot located in Oakwood.   This home features 3 Bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Stepping in, you are greeted with an OPEN floor plan with a great room with a cozy fireplace. Upgraded kitchen with granite countertops and new backsplash, ample updated cabinets and tile floors. Large master bedroom with WIC and renovated master bathroom. Additional bedroom nice size with large closets and full updated bath. Finished basement has a great living space, great for entertainment, a third bedroom, and an office. Basement also has its own A/C unit. New carpet throughout the home. End Unit providing privacy on upper deck and lower patio area. HOA takes care of landscaping. Owners have taken care of this home and taken care of it so that it can be cherished by its new owners! Located minutes from Lake Lanier, shopping, restaurants and I-985 and I-85. If you’re looking for a MOVE-IN ready home with privacy, then look no further! Too much to list—MUST SEE!
